          "partialFingerprints": {
            "primaryLocationLineHash": "ac2d3371fd137cd709607dc0cb17939b49c75a246605aaf9e943e320b2074063"
          },
          "level": "note"
        },
        {
          "ruleId": "A03",
          "message": {
            "text": ".claude/mcp-config.json contains {{PROJECT_PATH}} placeholders on lines 6 and 9. PROJECT_PATH is NOT in the canonical-12 placeholder list (.aod/scripts/bash/template-substitute.sh:50-63). Even after F-1 is fixed by switching init.sh to aod_template_substitute_placeholders, this placeholder will remain unsubstituted, leaving the MCP config non-functional and incomplete substitution surface across the personalization contract. The file appears to be an unwired example template \u2014 it is not actually loaded by any current Claude Code configuration in the repo."
          },
          "locations": [
